据这个邪恶的巫婆说...
if through this wicked witch's trick...

110
00:10:01,499 --> 00:10:03,958
你的手指会被一个纱锭扎破...
a spindle should your finger prick...

111
00:10:04,041 --> 00:10:07,251
或许这仍有一点希望...
a ray of hope there still may be in this...

112
00:10:07,334 --> 00:10:10,252
我给你的礼物
the gift I give to thee.

113
00:10:10,335 --> 00:10:13,003
不会死，你只是会在这个
Not in death, but just in sleep...

114
00:10:13,087 --> 00:10:15,504
致命的预言下沉睡...
the fateful prophecy you'll keep.

115
00:10:15,588 --> 00:10:17,963
当你得到真爱的吻时，魔咒就会破解...
And from this slumber you shall wake...

116
00:10:18,047 --> 00:10:21,466
