I'll turn her into a flower.

142
00:12:20,934 --> 00:12:24,434
- 巫婆吗? - 不是，亲爱的，是公主
- Maleficent? - Oh, no, dear. The princess.

143
00:12:24,518 --> 00:12:27,102
