还有洗衣服穿衣服哄她睡觉
And wash it and dress it and rock it to sleep.

172
00:14:01,309 --> 00:14:04,268
- 噢，我喜欢 - 你真的认为我们能吗?
- Oh, I'd love it. - Do you really think we can?

173
00:14:04,352 --> 00:14:06,519
人类可以，我们也可以
If humans can do it, so can we.

174
00:14:06,603 --> 00:14:10,021
- 我们还有魔法可以帮助我们 - 是的
- And we'd have our magic to help us. - That's right.

175
00:14:10,105 --> 00:14:13,398
不，不，不，不! 不许用魔法!
No, no, no, no, no, no! No magic!

176
00:14:13,481 --> 00:14:15,773
我要拿走这些魔法棒
I'll take those wands right now.

177
00:14:15,857 --> 00:14:18,358
最好也除去那些翅膀
Oh, better get rid of those wings too.

178
00:14:18,441 --> 00:14:22,567
你是说像凡人一样生活16年?
You mean live like mortals? For sixteen years?

179
00:14:22,652 --> 00:14:26,361
但是，现在，我们不知道行不行的通--
- Uh-huh. - B-Bu-- Now, now, we-- we don't know how.

180
00:14:26,445 --> 00:14:28,362
没有了魔法我们什么也不能做
We've never done anything without magic.

181
00:14:28,445 --> 00:14:30,821
这可以让巫婆不会怀疑--
And that's why Maleficent will never suspect--

182
00:14:30,905 --> 00:14:32,822
- 但是，但是，谁来洗衣服? - 还有做饭?
- But-- But who'll wash? - And cook?

183
00:14:32,906 --> 00:14:35,990
- 噢，我们大家一起努力 - 我来照顾孩子
- Oh, we'll all pitch in. - I'll take care of the baby.

184
00:14:36,074 --> 00:14:38,950
给我，亲爱的
Let me have it, dear.

185
00:14:39,033 --> 00:14:43,034
跟我来，我们必须立刻告诉国王
Come along now. We must tell Their Majesties at once.

186
00:14:46,578 --> 00:14:49,246
- 弗洛拉? - 弗洛拉?
- Flora? - Flora?

187
00:14:55,124 --> 00:14:58,542
所以国王和他的皇后怀着沉重的心情...
So the king and his queen watched with heavy hearts...

188
00:14:58,625 --> 00:15:02,167
看着他们唯一的最宝贵的女儿...
as their most precious possession, their only child...

189
00:15:02,252 --> 00:15:04,502
在那个夜晚消失
disappeared into the night.

190
00:15:17,175 --> 00:15:19,884
斯蒂芬国王和他的百姓...
Many sad and lonely years passed by...

191
00:15:19,968 --> 00:15:23,510
在悲哀和孤单中度过多年
for King Stefan and his people.

192
00:15:23,594 --> 00:15:27,720
但当公主16岁的生日邻近的时候...
But as the time for the princess' sixteenth birthday drew near...

193
00:15:27,804 --> 00:15:31,555
整个王国开始欣喜若狂
the entire kingdom began to rejoice.

194
00:15:31,639 --> 00:15:35,223
因为众所周知，只要巫婆的领域...
For everyone knew that as long as Maleficent's domain...

195
00:15:35,307 --> 00:15:39,976
那座禁止的山，因为她的暴怒和挫折发出如雷之声...
the Forbidden Mountains, thundered with her wrath and frustration...

196
00:15:40,059 --> 00:15:43,144
她邪恶的预言就不会实现
her evil prophecy had not yet been fulfilled.

197
00:15:54,858 --> 00:15:57,525
难以置信！
It's incredible!

198
00:15:57,608 --> 00:16:01,484
16年了，居然一点消息也没有
Sixteen years, and not a trace of her.

199
00:16:01,569 --> 00:16:04,903
她不会消失得无影无踪 !
She couldn't have vanished into thin air!

200
00:16:04,987 --> 00:16:08,988
你们确信每一处地方都搜查过了?
Are you sure you searched everywhere?

201
00:16:09,072 --> 00:16:11,406
是的，是的，都搜查过了
Yes, yes, uh, everywhere.

202
00:16:11,489 --> 00:16:13,489
- 我们都搜查过了 - 是的，是的！
- We all did. - Yeah, yeah!

203
00:16:13,574 --> 00:16:15,657
是的
Uh-huh, yeah.

204
00:16:15,741 --> 00:16:18,534
市镇呢? 森林? 深山?
And what about the town? The forest? The mountains?

205
00:16:18,617 --> 00:16:21,827
是的，我们搜查过深山 嗯，森林...
Yeah, we searched mountains, uh, uh, uh, uh, forests...

206
00:16:21,910 --> 00:16:24,536
还有，住宅，还有--
and, uh, houses, and, uh--

207
00:16:24,620 --> 00:16:27,496
让我想想，还有所有的摇篮
Let me see. Uh, and all the cradles.

208
00:16:27,580 --> 00:16:30,998
- 摇篮? - 是的
- Cradle? - Yep, yep.

209
00:16:31,081 --> 00:16:33,206
每个摇篮
Every cradle.

210
00:16:33,291 --> 00:16:35,791
摇篮?
Cradle?

211
00:16:35,875 --> 00:16:38,458
你听到了吗，我的宝贝?
Did you hear that, my pet?

212
00:16:38,543 --> 00:16:43,295
这些年来，他们一直在寻找一个婴儿
All these years, they've been looking for a baby.

213
00:16:55,091 --> 00:16:57,508
傻瓜!
Fools!

214
00:16:57,593 --> 00:17:00,677
白痴! 笨蛋!
Idiots! Imbeciles!

215
00:17:15,933 --> 00:17:18,017
噢，他们不可救药了
Oh, they're hopeless.

216
00:17:18,101 --> 00:17:21,685
这简直是邪恶势力的耻辱
A disgrace to the forces of evil.

217
00:17:24,021 --> 00:17:28,355
宝贝，你是我最后的希望了
My pet, you are my last hope.

218
00:17:28,439 --> 00:17:31,189
到处飞一下
Circle far and wide.

219
00:17:31,274 --> 00:17:33,941
搜查一个16岁的少女...
Search for a maid of sixteen...

220
00:17:34,025 --> 00:17:36,358
有着金黄色的头发...
with hair of sunshine gold...

221
00:17:36,443 --> 00:17:39,235
和玫瑰红色的嘴唇
and lips red as the rose.

222
00:17:39,319 --> 00:17:42,861
去吧，别让我失望
Go, and do not fail me.

223
00:17:48,156 --> 00:17:50,614
16年来...
And so, for sixteen long years...

224
00:17:50,698 --> 00:17:54,116
公主的行踪一直保持的很神秘
the whereabouts of the princess remained a mystery.

225
00:17:54,199 --> 00:17:57,326
在森林深处的一座砍柴者的农舍内...
While deep in the forest in a woodcutter's cottage...

226
00:17:57,410 --> 00:18:01,202
那些仙女正在执行她们安排得很好的计划
the good fairies carried out their well-laid plan.

227
00:18:01,286 --> 00:18:04,995
象凡人一样生活，她们对她就像自己的孩子那样养育...
Living like mortals, they had reared the child as their own...

228
00:18:05,079 --> 00:18:08,497
她们叫她布莱尔罗丝
and called her Briar Rose.

229
00:18:12,541 --> 00:18:15,000
今天，她16岁的生日...
On this, her sixteenth birthday...

230
00:18:15,084 --> 00:18:17,335
仙女们打算办一个舞会...
the good fairies had planned a party...

231
00:18:17,418 --> 00:18:21,461
给她一个意想不到的惊喜
and something extra special for a surprise.

232
00:18:21,545 --> 00:18:24,629
- 那么，这个呢? - 这个是我选的
- Well, now, how about this one? - This is the one I picked.

233
00:18:24,713 --> 00:18:26,755
噢，她穿起来一定很漂亮
Oh, she'll look beautiful in that.

234
00:18:26,839 --> 00:18:29,298
- 我认为这应该做点改变
- Now, I thought a few changes here. - Uh-huh.

235
00:18:29,381 --> 00:18:32,965
- 别忘了一漂亮的弓 - 是的，举起这肩线
- And don't forget a pretty bow. - Yes, and raise the shoulder line.

236
00:18:33,050 --> 00:18:35,425
- 我们把它做成蓝色的 - 不，还是粉红色
- We'll make it blue. - Oh, no, dear, pink.

237
00:18:35,509 --> 00:18:37,426
- 但是-- - 当然，我们得需要少许褶
- But-- - Of course, we'll need a few pleats.

238
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:39,886
但是我们怎样让她离开这个房子?
Yes, but how are we gonna get her out of the house?

239
00:18:39,969 --> 00:18:42,094
我在考虑
Oh, I'll think of something.

240
00:18:42,179 --> 00:18:45,971
你们三个一直在干什么?
Well, and what are you three dears up to?

241
00:18:46,056 --> 00:18:48,181
-什么?
- Up to? - Up to? - Up to?

242
00:18:50,307 --> 00:18:52,640
我们，我们--
Well, we-- Uh, we-- W-We--

243
00:18:52,725 --> 00:18:56,684
- 我们想你去采些浆果 - 对，浆果！
- We want you to pick some berries. - That's it, berries!

244
00:18:56,769 --> 00:18:59,144
- 浆果? - 很多浆果
- Berries? - Lots of berries.

245
00:18:59,227 --> 00:19:03,353
- 但我昨天已经采过浆果了 - 噢，我们还需要，亲爱的
- But I-I picked berries yesterday. - Oh, w-we need more, dear.

246
00:19:03,438 --> 00:19:06,481
- 很多，很多 - 是的!
- Lots, lots more. - Yes!

247
00:19:07,898 --> 00:19:10,982
- 别急着回来，亲爱的 - 但也别走太远了
- Now don't hurry back, dear. - But don't go too far.

248
00:19:11,065 --> 00:19:13,483
- 别和陌生人讲话 - 再见，亲爱的
- And don't speak to strangers. - Goodbye, dear.

249
00:19:13,567 --> 00:19:17,027
再见!
- Goodbye! - Goodbye! - Goodbye!

250
00:19:18,527 --> 00:19:21,987
- 我想知道她是否怀疑了 - 当然没有
- I wonder if she suspects. - Of course not.

251
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:25,405
来吧，她会惊喜的
Come on! Oh, will she be surprised.

252
00:19:25,489 --> 00:19:27,572
一个生日宴会
A real birthday party.

253
00:19:27,656 --> 00:19:29,615
还有生日蛋糕
With a real birthday cake.

254
00:19:29,699 --> 00:19:32,575
一件服装一位公主，够让我们骄傲了
Yes, and a dress a princess can be proud of.

255
00:19:32,658 --> 00:19:36,826
- 我去拿魔法棒 - 好的，噢，魔法棒？
- I'll get the wands. - Yes, you can, uh-- The wands?

256
00:19:36,911 --> 00:19:39,703
- 不要 - 不许用魔法！
- Oh, no! - No magic!

257
00:19:39,787 --> 00:19:42,162
但是16年马上就要过去了
But the sixteen years are almost over.

258
00:19:42,246 --> 00:19:44,413
我们要以防万一
We're taking no chances.

259
00:19:44,497 --> 00:19:47,414
但我从未烤过奇特的蛋糕
But I've never baked a fancy cake.

260
00:19:47,499 --> 00:19:49,540
你不必烤那样的蛋糕，亲爱的
Oh, you won't have to, dear.

261
00:19:49,624 --> 00:19:51,749
我去烤蛋糕
I'm going to bake the cake.

262
00:19:51,833 --> 00:19:54,501
- 你? - 她早就就想烤了
- You? - Oh, she's always wanted to, dear.

263
00:19:54,584 --> 00:19:57,001
- 这是她最后的机会
- And this is her last chance. - Well--

264
00:19:57,085 --> 00:20:00,878
我将要用粉红色和蓝色的勿忘我烤个15层的蛋糕
I'm going to make it fifteen layers with pink and blue forget-me-nots.

265
00:20:00,962 --> 00:20:03,379
我去做衣服
And I'm making the dress.

266
00:20:03,463 --> 00:20:06,506
但你不会缝制，她也从未烤过蛋糕
But you can't sew, and she's never cooked.

267
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:10,382
- 很简单！ - 照着这本书做就行了
- Oh-ho-ho, it's simple! - All you do is follow the book.

268
00:20:10,466 --> 00:20:14,300
站上来，亲爱的，你暂时做会模特
Up here, dear. You can be the dummy.

269
00:20:14,384 --> 00:20:17,885
该我说我们还是应该使用魔法
Well, I still say we ought to use magic.

270
00:20:24,347 --> 00:20:27,264
"面粉，三杯"
"Flour, three cups."

271
00:20:27,349 --> 00:20:30,350
杯子，杯子，杯子...
Cups, cups, cups, cups, cups, cups, cups.

272
00:20:30,433 --> 00:20:33,267
噢
Oh.

273
00:20:33,351 --> 00:20:36,519
一，二，三
One, two, three.

274
00:20:36,602 --> 00:20:40,603
- 这用来干什么? - 它在底部要有一个洞
- What's that for? - Well, it's got to have a hole in the bottom.

275
00:20:40,687 --> 00:20:44,105
那是为了脚能穿过
That's for the feet to go through.

276
00:20:46,190 --> 00:20:49,608
- 它是粉色的 - 喔，可爱的图案，不是吗?
- It's pink. - Oh, lovely shade, isn't it?

277
00:20:49,691 --> 00:20:53,359
- 但我喜欢蓝色的 - 现在，亲爱的...
- But I wanted it blue. - Now, dear...

278
00:20:53,443 --> 00:20:55,652
我们决定粉色作为她的颜色
we decided pink was her colour.

279
00:20:55,735 --> 00:20:58,819
你说了算!
You decided!

280
00:21:09,741 --> 00:21:13,700
"两个鸡蛋，逐渐的拌入"
"Two eggs. Fold in gently."

281
00:21:13,785 --> 00:21:16,410
压碎？喔，好的
Fold? Uh, oh, well.

282
00:21:20,955 --> 00:21:24,039
我不能呼吸了!
I can't breathe!

283
00:21:24,122 --> 00:21:26,790
让我出去
Let me out of here.

284
00:21:28,625 --> 00:21:32,125
- 看起来很可怕 - 那是因为穿在你身上，亲爱的
- It looks awful. - That's because it's on you, dear.

285
00:21:32,209 --> 00:21:35,627
"现在，一茶匙发酵粉" "茶匙"?
"Now, yeast, one tsp." "Tsp."?

286
00:21:35,710 --> 00:21:37,961
一茶匙
One teaspoon.

287
00:21:38,045 --> 00:21:41,046
- 当然，一茶匙 - 嗯!
- Oh, one teaspoon, of course! - Hmm!

288
00:21:47,383 --> 00:21:50,842
喔，那孩子长的真快
Oh, gracious, how that child has grown.

289
00:21:50,926 --> 00:21:54,260
好像我们昨天才带她来这似的
Oh, it seems only yesterday we brought her here.

290
00:21:54,344 --> 00:21:57,053
只是一个婴儿
Just a tiny baby.

291
00:21:59,972 --> 00:22:03,889
- 怎么了，玛莉怀德 - 究竟怎么了，亲爱的?
- Why, Merryweather. - What ever is the matter, dear?

292
00:22:03,973 --> 00:22:06,473
过了今天，她就要成为一位公主了...
After today, she'll be a princess...

293
00:22:06,557 --> 00:22:09,392
我们不会再有布莱尔罗丝了
and we won't have any Briar Rose.

294
00:22:09,475 --> 00:22:11,767
- 噢，弗洛拉! - 现在，现在...
- Oh, Flora! - Now, now, now, now.

295
00:22:11,851 --> 00:22:15,560
我们，我们都知道这一天迟早会到来
Well, we-- we all knew this day had to come.

296
00:22:15,645 --> 00:22:18,396
但为什么要来的这么快呢?
But why did it have to come so soon?

297
00:22:18,479 --> 00:22:22,522
毕竟，我们拥有她16年
After all, we've had her for sixteen years.

298
00:22:22,606 --> 00:22:25,023
美好的16年
Sixteen wonderful years.

299
00:22:28,441 --> 00:22:31,901
我们的所做正如许多的傻子所为
Oh, gracious! We're acting like a lot of ninnies.

300
00:22:31,984 --> 00:22:35,902
快点，否则我们准备好之前她会回来的
Come on. She'll be back before we get started.

301
00:24:22,198 --> 00:24:25,074
你听见了吗，参森？
You hear that, Samson?

302
00:24:25,158 --> 00:24:27,616
很动听
Beautiful.

303
00:24:30,702 --> 00:24:32,952
谁在唱?
What is it?

304
00:24:33,036 --> 00:24:36,620
来吧，我们去探个究竟
Come on. Let's find out.

305
00:24:36,705 --> 00:24:40,247
喔，别这样 额外的一桶燕麦？
Aw, come on. For an extra bucket of oats?

306
00:24:41,665 --> 00:24:45,125
再加一些胡萝卜?
And a few carrots?

307
00:24:45,208 --> 00:24:47,584
驾!
Hup, boy!

308
00:25:17,055 --> 00:25:19,598
哇哦
Whoa!

309
00:25:31,603 --> 00:25:33,936
别再想吃胡萝卜
No carrots.

310
00:25:46,067 --> 00:25:49,402
我想知道
I wonder

311
00:25:49,485 --> 00:25:52,904
我想知道

