我想知道为什么每只小鸟
I wonder why each little bird

313
00:25:57,363 --> 00:25:59,989
有某人
Has a someone

314
00:26:00,073 --> 00:26:03,158
来歌唱那
To sing to

315
00:26:03,241 --> 00:26:06,451
美好事物
Sweet things to

316
00:26:06,534 --> 00:26:11,952
一首快活的小爱曲
A gay little love melody

317
00:26:14,204 --> 00:26:17,623
我想知道
I wonder

318
00:26:17,706 --> 00:26:20,582
我想知道

319
00:26:20,665 --> 00:26:24,291
如果我的心一直唱歌
Ifmy heart keeps singing

320
00:26:24,375 --> 00:26:28,084
我的歌声会飞向
Will my song go winging

321
00:26:28,169 --> 00:26:31,462
某人
To someone

322
00:26:31,545 --> 00:26:35,087
一个会找到我的人
Who 'll find me

323
00:26:35,172 --> 00:26:40,632
然后他也会对我
And bring back a love song

324
00:26:40,716 --> 00:26:44,967
唱情歌
To me

325
00:26:49,677 --> 00:26:51,927
噢，亲爱的
Oh, dear.

326
00:26:52,012 --> 00:26:55,846
为什么她们仍然把我看作是小孩呢?
Why do they still treat me like a child?

327
00:26:57,181 --> 00:26:59,348
谁?
Who?

328
00:26:59,432 --> 00:27:03,558
弗洛拉，弗娜还有玛莉怀德阿姨
Aunt Flora and Fauna and Merryweather.

329
00:27:05,517 --> 00:27:08,602
她们从不让我接触任何人
They never want me to meet anyone.

330
00:27:12,729 --> 00:27:14,937
但是你知道吗?
But you know something?

331
00:27:15,022 --> 00:27:17,230
我骗了她们
I fooled them.

332
00:27:17,315 --> 00:27:19,940
我接触过某人
I have met someone.

333
00:27:20,024 --> 00:27:21,815
谁?
Who?

334
00:27:24,525 --> 00:27:27,026
谁? 谁?
Who? Who?

335
00:27:27,110 --> 00:27:30,070
一位王子
Oh, a prince.

336
00:27:32,071 --> 00:27:36,197
他高大英俊，还有--
Well, he's tall and handsome and--

337
00:27:36,281 --> 00:27:38,281
