and so romantic.

338
00:27:41,075 --> 00:27:45,785
我们一起散布一起聊天
Oh, we walk together and talk together.

339
00:27:45,868 --> 00:27:49,036
在我们说再见之前...
And just before we say goodbye...

340
00:27:49,119 --> 00:27:51,995
他拥抱我...
he takes me in his arms...

341
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:55,289
然后...
and then...

342
00:27:55,372 --> 00:27:57,664
我醒来了
I wake up.

