01:03:21,434 --> 01:03:23,977
时光匆匆的过去
The years roll by.

691
01:03:24,062 --> 01:03:29,108
但是，几百年对一颗坚定的心来说就像只有一天
But a hundred years to a steadfast heart are but a day.

692
01:03:29,192 --> 01:03:32,986
现在，地牢的大门....
And now, the gates of a dungeon part...

693
01:03:33,071 --> 01:03:37,699
已经开了，我们的王子也可以出发了
and our prince is free to go his way.

694
01:03:37,784 --> 01:03:41,787
骑上他的马
Off he rides on his noble steed--

695
01:03:41,870 --> 01:03:46,207
一个勇敢的高大的身躯，
a valiant figure, straight and tall--

696
01:03:46,291 --> 01:03:48,501
将要唤醒他的爱....
to wake his love...

697
01:03:48,585 --> 01:03:52,004
献出第一次爱的吻....
with love's first kiss...

698
01:03:52,089 --> 01:03:57,301
他将证明真爱会战胜一切！
and prove that true love conquers all!

699
01:04:00,722 --> 01:04:03,474
为什么，你，你--
Why, you, you, y--

700
01:04:06,894 --> 01:04:10,647
来吧，宝贝，我们离开高贵的公主...
Come, my pet. Let us leave our noble prince...

701
01:04:10,731 --> 01:04:14,151
随着这些愉快的想法
with these happy thoughts.

702
01:04:17,738 --> 01:04:20,949
这是最快乐的一天
A most gratifying day.

703
01:04:25,705 --> 01:04:28,874
16年来第一次...
For the first time in sixteen years...

704
01:04:28,957 --> 01:04:32,126
我会睡的很香
I shall sleep well.

705
01:04:47,767 --> 01:04:50,352
没有时间解释了
Shh! No time to explain.

706
01:04:59,278 --> 01:05:02,030
等等，菲利普王子，真爱之路...
Wait, Prince Phillip. The road to true love...

707
01:05:02,114 --> 01:05:05,158
可能仍然被很多的危险阻碍...
may be barred by still many more dangers...

708
01:05:05,242 --> 01:05:07,452
你必须自己单独去面对
which you alone will have to face.

709
01:05:07,536 --> 01:05:12,373
因此你要装备这块坚固的魔法盾牌...
So arm thyselfwith this enchanted shield ofvirtue...

710
01:05:12,457 --> 01:05:15,709
和这把锋利的真理之剑...
and this mighty sword of truth...

711
01:05:15,793 --> 01:05:20,047
用这些正义的武器将战胜邪恶
for these weapons of righteousness will triumph over evil.

712
01:05:20,131 --> 01:05:22,799
现在，我们得抓紧时间
Now, come. We must hurry.

713
01:06:09,929 --> 01:06:12,055
菲利普，当心！
Phillip, watch out!

714
01:07:08,526 --> 01:07:12,737
安静！你，告诉那些愚蠢的人--
Silence! You, tell those fools to--

715
01:07:12,822 --> 01:07:16,241
不！不！
No! No!

716
01:07:19,745 --> 01:07:22,914
小心，菲利普！
Watch out, Phillip!

717
01:07:29,671 --> 01:07:32,923
快点！快点，菲利普！
Hurry! Hurry, Phillip!

718
01:07:44,519 --> 01:07:48,355
荆棘满布的森林将是他的坟墓...
A forest of thorns shall be his tomb...

719
01:07:48,439 --> 01:07:51,900
布满毁灭的雾穿过天空忍受!
borne through the skies on a fog of doom!

720
01:07:51,984 --> 01:07:55,486
现在，伴随着诅咒，一切都在我掌握之中
Now go with a curse and serve me well.

721
01:07:55,571 --> 01:07:59,365
斯蒂芬的城堡周围布满我的符咒
'Round Stefan's castle cast my spell.

722
01:08:50,248 --> 01:08:52,959
不！这不可能！
No! It cannot be!

723
01:08:58,756 --> 01:09:02,717
现在你要面对的是我，王子...
Now shall you deal with me, O Prince...

724
01:09:02,802 --> 01:09:05,512
地狱的全部力量!
and all the powers of hell!

725
01:09:50,806 --> 01:09:53,391
上来，沿着这上来!
Up! Up this way!

726
01:10:09,157 --> 01:10:11,908
现在，真理之剑，飞跃雨燕...
Now, sword of truth, fly swift and sure...

727
01:10:11,993 --> 01:10:15,495
确信邪恶灭亡，真理永存！
that evil die and good endure!

728
01:11:57,843 --> 01:11:59,928
啊--噢，噢
Ehhh-- Oh, oh, uh--

729
01:12:00,012 --> 01:12:04,099
原谅我，休伯特。葡萄酒，现在，嗯--
Forgive me, Hubert. Ehh, uh, the wine. Now, uh--

730
01:12:04,183 --> 01:12:06,142
g你，在说话吗?
You, uh, were saying?

731
01:12:06,227 --> 01:12:10,146
啊? 我在说吗？ 噢，噢，是的
Huh? I-I was? Oh! Oh, yes.

732
01:12:10,231 --> 01:12:14,985
毕竟，斯蒂芬，这是十四世纪
Well, after all, Stefan, this is the fourteenth century.

733
01:12:15,069 --> 01:12:18,321
是的，你，你刚才已经说过了
Yes. You, uh, you said that a moment ago.

734
01:12:18,405 --> 01:12:21,448
回到刚才的主题...
Well, to come right to the point...

735
01:12:21,533 --> 01:12:24,326
我儿子菲利普说他要结婚，和--
my son Phillip says he's going to marry--

736
01:12:50,102 --> 01:12:52,895
是奥罗拉!她在这！
It's Aurora! She's here!

737
01:12:57,317 --> 01:13:00,111
还有菲利普!
A-And-And-And Phillip!

738
01:13:14,167 --> 01:13:17,085
这是怎么回事，孩子?
Wh-- What does this mean, boy?

739
01:13:17,170 --> 01:13:19,921
我不明白--
I-I don't under--

740
01:13:22,716 --> 01:13:25,551
但，但是--
B-Bu-- But-But, uh--

741
01:13:31,516 --> 01:13:34,101
我，我不明白
I-I don't understand.

742
01:13:58,501 --> 01:14:01,586
怎么了，弗娜，亲爱的?
Why, Fauna, what's the matter, dear?

743
01:14:01,670 --> 01:14:05,465
噢，我只是替这个结局高兴
Oh, I just love happy endings.

744
01:14:05,549 --> 01:14:09,427
是的，我也是--
Yes, I do too-- t--

745
01:14:09,510 --> 01:14:11,762
蓝色!
Blue!

746
01:14:15,058 --> 01:14:19,019
- 粉色 - 我认识你
- Pink. - I knowyou

747
01:14:19,103 --> 01:14:24,399
- 我曾经在梦境中和你一起散步 - 蓝色
- I walked with you once upon a dream - Blue.

748
01:14:24,484 --> 01:14:27,027
我认识你
I knowyou

749
01:14:27,111 --> 01:14:29,071
你的眼神
The gleam in your eyes

750
01:14:29,155 --> 01:14:32,407
是如此的熟悉
Is so familiar a gleam

751
01:14:32,491 --> 01:14:35,451
但我知道是真实的
Yet I know it's true

752
01:14:35,535 --> 01:14:40,331
那梦境是他们很少见到的
That visions are seldom all they seem

753
01:14:40,415 --> 01:14:42,792
但是如果我认识你
But ifl knowyou

754
01:14:42,876 --> 01:14:45,002
我知道你会怎么做
I know what you'll do

755
01:14:45,087 --> 01:14:47,088
你会立刻爱上我
You'll love me at once

756
01:14:47,172 --> 01:14:49,257
你会这么做
The wayyou did once

757
01:14:49,341 --> 01:14:51,884
在那个
Upon

758
01:14:51,969 --> 01:15:00,476
梦里
A dream

